# TripMappa

Road trip planning app — [tripmappa.com](https://tripmappa.com).  
Founder: Cade Warmke (cadewarmke@gmail.com).

## Stack

React/Vite, Vercel, Supabase, Claude Sonnet, Google Maps/Places, HERE Maps, Stripe, Resend, Twilio, NREL, Weather.gov.

## Tiers

| Tier | Price | Trips |
|------|-------|-------|
| Wanderer | free | 3 |
| Voyager | $4.99/mo | 20 |
| Trailblazer | $9.99/mo | 100 |
| Founder | first 1000 users | 1 year free Trailblazer + gold star badge |

## Design

- Gold `#FFD28C`, Orange `#FF8C42`, Night `#0D0A1A`, Day `#FDF3E0`
- **Fraunces** for UI; **Limelight** for neon signs only
- No purple. No glass morphism. No Tailwind.
- No AI language in user-facing copy

## Workflow

- **v0 generates** all UI components; **Cursor integrates only**
- **One fix per prompt** for shared files
- **Verify on tripmappa.com** after every deploy
- **Never break** generation or flow logic

## Admin

`cadewarmke@gmail.com` bypasses all limits.
